Interface SignInResultHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultSignInResultHandler

    public interface SignInResultHandler
    Interface for handling results from calling IdentityManager's signInOrSignUp().

      • onIntermediateProviderCancel

        void onIntermediateProviderCancel(android.app.Activity callingActivity,

      • onIntermediateProviderError

        ex - the exception that occurred.
